<template>
  <button
    id="logout-button"
    @click.prevent="handleLogout"
    :disabled="isLoggedOut"
  >
    Log out
  </button>

</template>

<script>
  Userfront.init("demo1234");

  export default {
    methods: {
      handleLogout() {
        Userfront.logout();
      },
    },
    computed: {
      isLoggedOut() {
        return !Userfront.tokens.accessToken;
      },
    },
  };
  //ako korisnik jeste ulogovan tj moze da se izloguje bice zeleno
  //
</script>

<style scoped>
  
  #logout-button {
    background-color: green;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 5px 10px;
  }
	
  
  #logout-button[disabled] {
    background-color: white;
    color: lightgrey;
  }
</style>
